%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Speech_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 991c04154cea34203a64a5fe4f5e097e, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 2889047881015296
    m_Localized: Theo
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889048443052032
    m_Localized: Hey Francis!  Looking to save your progress so far?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889048552103936
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889048648572928
    m_Localized: Yes, please!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889048753430528
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889048849899520
    m_Localized: No, thank you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889048950562816
    m_Localized: Default
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049051226112
    m_Localized: Root Node Skipped
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049147695104
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049244164096
    m_Localized: What's that?  You say you saw me at the PortaBank (TM)?  I don't
      know what you're talking about, I work here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049344827392
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049441296384
    m_Localized: Aside from you and Horse, I'm literally the only person who does
      work around here
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049541959680
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049638428672
    m_Localized: You want the key to the ballpit?  Alright, let's tango.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049739091968
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049835560960
    m_Localized: Hi Tilly, nice hair, I mean, nice outfit, I mean . . . anyway, did
      you want to hang out this weekend?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889049936224256
    m_Localized: Steve5000
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050032693248
    m_Localized: Root Node Skipped
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050129162240
    m_Localized: Steve5000
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050229825536
    m_Localized: Oh, hey Francis . . . err, Frankie.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050326294528
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050426957824
    m_Localized: Uh . . . what the hell was that?  What ARE you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050523426816
    m_Localized: Steve5000
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050624090112
    m_Localized: Did you forget your key card again?  You can borrow mine, I'm just
      on my way out.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050720559104
    m_Localized: Steve5000
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050821222400
    m_Localized: Hey, look -- before you go in there, you should know -- the interns
      have been acting really weird.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889050917691392
    m_Localized: Steve5000
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051018354688
    m_Localized: Let's brush up your combat skills, I don't want you to get embarrassed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051119017984
    m_Localized: Steve5000
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051215486976
    m_Localized: Not sure what you're talkin' about buddy!  Why don't you get in
      there and show them who's boss?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051316150272
    m_Localized: Hipster
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051412619264
    m_Localized: Skip
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051513282560
    m_Localized: Hipster
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051609751552
    m_Localized: This elevator is broken.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051706220544
    m_Localized: Hipster
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051806883840
    m_Localized: I think the electrical breaker tripped and needs to be reset, but
      it's in the basement and the workers here have kinda gone mad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889051903352832
    m_Localized: Hipster
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052004016128
    m_Localized: Yeehaw, you did it!  You madman, you really gosh darn did it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052104679424
    m_Localized: Hipster
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052205342720
    m_Localized: Maybe you could go check it out?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052306006016
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052419252224
    m_Localized: Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052524109824
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052628967424
    m_Localized: I got these neat refurbished portable sheds on discount!  Can you
      believe it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052729630720
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052830294016
    m_Localized: Oh, did you want me to save your progress so far?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889052930957312
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053031620608
    m_Localized: Sure!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053136478208
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053237141504
    m_Localized: Nah, not today
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053337804800
    m_Localized: Beguiled Monk
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053438468096
    m_Localized: I'm so aerodynamic!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053539131392
    m_Localized: L'il Slugger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053652377600
    m_Localized: Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053761429504
    m_Localized: L'il Slugger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053870481408
    m_Localized: What?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889053983727616
    m_Localized: L'il Slugger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889054088585216
    m_Localized: So what?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889054206025728
    m_Localized: L'il Slugger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889054319271936
    m_Localized: Get bent.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889054432518144
    m_Localized: L'il Slugger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889054545764352
    m_Localized: Friggin' nerd!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889054659010560
    m_Localized: Bewitched Monk
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889054776451072
    m_Localized: Less hair, more brain cells.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889054889697280
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889055002943488
    m_Localized: Wait!  Don't hurt me, I'm not your average Vole!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889055116189696
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889055229435904
    m_Localized: I may be a small rodent, but my mind is vast and my experiences
      multitudinous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889055338487808
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889055451734016
    m_Localized: Now, down to business.  You -- yes YOU, behind the keyboard -- you
      should be aware that your enemies won't wait for their turn.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889055564980224
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889055678226432
    m_Localized: So study up before your fights -- you can see what you can do by
      pressing Tab and selecting Abilities.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889055791472640
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889055900524544
    m_Localized: In battle, select which ability you want with your "W-A-S-D" keys
      and then lock it in with "E".
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889056017965056
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889056131211264
    m_Localized: 'I hope this makes sense -- I don''t actually speak your language. 
      I''m just reciting what I read by reading the Official Frankie Game Manual
      (TM).  '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889056248651776
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889056357703680
    m_Localized: This is the last sentence I memorized.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889056466755584
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889056575807488
    m_Localized: Squeak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889056684859392
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889056798105600
    m_Localized: Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889056911351808
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057020403712
    m_Localized: ' I got this car freshener tree here to help freshen things up! 
      So, do you feel FRESH?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057133649920
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057242701824
    m_Localized: Oh, did you want me to save your progress so far?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057355948032
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057460805632
    m_Localized: Sure!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057569857536
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057674715136
    m_Localized: Nah, not today
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057775378432
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057880236032
    m_Localized: '*thwrp* Don''t get too close. *pfft*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889057980899328
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889058085756928
    m_Localized: I just farted . . . *blaaat*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889058190614528
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889058291277824
    m_Localized: '*pbbbt* Maybe the chili last night was a bad idea. *poot*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889058391941120
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889058496798720
    m_Localized: Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889058597462016
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889058702319616
    m_Localized: HI!  Welcome to PortaBank (TM)!  Your number one portable banking
      solution!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889058802982912
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889058903646208
    m_Localized: Oh, did you want me to save your progress so far?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059004309504
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059109167104
    m_Localized: Sure!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059209830400
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059314688000
    m_Localized: Nah, not today
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059419545600
    m_Localized: Pretty Girl
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059520208896
    m_Localized: Wow!  You actually made it through the forest?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059620872192
    m_Localized: Pretty Girl
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059717341184
    m_Localized: A squirrel looked at me weird.  Now I'm too scared to even step
      foot in there.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059818004480
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889059918667776
    m_Localized: root node
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060019331072
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060115800064
    m_Localized: '*cough* *hrkkk* Well . . . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060216463360
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060317126656
    m_Localized: There's nothing left to do here . . . Goodbye Phil.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060417789952
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060518453248
    m_Localized: Looks like this is it for me.  I hoped I could bring you further.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060614922240
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060715585536
    m_Localized: Looks like plain old ordinary trash.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060816248832
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889060912717824
    m_Localized: I guess I'm just a cup of ramen after all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061013381120
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061114044416
    m_Localized: 'Oh, I almost forgot -- my dying words:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061214707712
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061311176704
    m_Localized: Listen, this world - your world - is not what it appears to be. 
      You must have noticed by now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061411840000
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061512503296
    m_Localized: This miasma threatens everything you know.  You must find out what,
      or who, is behind it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061613166592
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061709635584
    m_Localized: The answer lies in your own memories.  You must go on a journey
      in search of your 10 curios of power to unlock the truth.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061810298880
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889061915156480
    m_Localized: You'll meet many friends along the way.  Trust in them, rely on
      them.  You need their help to make it through this.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062015819776
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062116483072
    m_Localized: Go now.  Your first curio, I sense that it is close.  Somewhere
      in the nearby suburb of Prim.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062217146368
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062317809664
    m_Localized: The subway should take you there.  Wait, you should know this, you
      live in Prim, DON'T YOU?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062418472960
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062519136256
    m_Localized: Oh man, oh boy, I see the light.  This is really it now.  Before
      I go, did you listen closely enough, or do you want me to repeat this?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062623993856
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062728851456
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062833709056
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889062934372352
    m_Localized: No
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063035035648
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063139893248
    m_Localized: Oh . . . really?  Honestly, I'm barely holding on here.  Ok, I guess,
      here goes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063240556544
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063345414144
    m_Localized: Alright.  Well, you're a smart, capable, and brave man, Frankie. 
      Remember that.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063446077440
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063550935040
    m_Localized: I'm glad I got to meet you.  *squish* *slurp* *bye*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063655792640
    m_Localized: Default
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063760650240
    m_Localized: Default Text to Overwrite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063865507840
    m_Localized: Fancy Lady
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889063970365440
    m_Localized: Is that boy still hanging around my house?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889064079417344
    m_Localized: Fancy Lady
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889064180080640
    m_Localized: I'm his mom, but to be honest, I wish he'd just leave me alone
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889064293326848
    m_Localized: Fancy Lady
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889064398184448
    m_Localized: What a bother
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889064503042048
    m_Localized: Some Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889064612093952
    m_Localized: Root Node
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889064712757248
    m_Localized: Some Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889064821809152
    m_Localized: Hey
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889064926666752
    m_Localized: Some Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889065035718656
    m_Localized: My parents said I'd grow up to be famous.  I only have a modest
      social media presence though.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889065140576256
    m_Localized: Some Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889065245433856
    m_Localized: Don't let the voles into your house
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889065354485760
    m_Localized: Some Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889065459343360
    m_Localized: They seem nice, but they'll eat right through your electrical wiring
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889065568395264
    m_Localized: Some Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889065673252864
    m_Localized: I really like your style
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889065782304768
    m_Localized: Bald Man
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889065887162368
    m_Localized: Wow, you really trekked all the way up here?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
