    m_Localized: Default
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889076511334400
    m_Localized: Default Text to Overwrite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889076611997696
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889076712660992
    m_Localized: Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889076813324288
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889076913987584
    m_Localized: I remember what I needed to tell you now, but it wasn't that important.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077014650880
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077115314176
    m_Localized: I need to tell you something urgently!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077220171776
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077333417984
    m_Localized: Uh.  Hmmm...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077442469888
    m_Localized: Hipster Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077543133184
    m_Localized: I forgot.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077643796480
    m_Localized: Lil Slugger
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077744459776
    m_Localized: I wanna get a slushie from the Chug'n'Slurp (TM), but mom says the
      forest is too dangerous
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077845123072
    m_Localized: Charlie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889077945786368
    m_Localized: It's a little cramped, but you can have a nap in our bed with us
      if you want?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078046449664
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078147112960
    m_Localized: Ok!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078251970560
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078352633856
    m_Localized: Nah.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078453297152
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078553960448
    m_Localized: Root Node
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078667206656
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078767869952
    m_Localized: You brought me hot sauce and chopsticks!  Great!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078868533248
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889078973390848
    m_Localized: Wai-  *he grabs the chopsticks and hot sauce*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079074054144
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079174717440
    m_Localized: I'm really hungry from all that cardio!  Luckily someone made this
      delicious ramen and just left it here!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079275380736
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079376044032
    m_Localized: No, you'-
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079480901632
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079581564928
    m_Localized: '*rip* *pour* *swish* *sluuuuuuuurrrp*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079678033920
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079782891520
    m_Localized: Oh my go-
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079883554816
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889079984218112
    m_Localized: Team work is the dream work, am I right?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080084881408
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080185544704
    m_Localized: I'm soooo full.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080286208000
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080386871296
    m_Localized: '*sluuuuurp* *chomp* *toss*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080487534592
    m_Localized: Porta Attendant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080592392192
    m_Localized: Skip Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080693055488
    m_Localized: Porta Attendant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080789524480
    m_Localized: HI!  Welcome to PortaBank (TM)!  Your number one portable banking
      solution!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080894382080
    m_Localized: Porta Attendant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889080990851072
    m_Localized: Let me know if you have any questions!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081095708672
    m_Localized: Porta Attendant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081196371968
    m_Localized: I got these neat refurbished portable sheds on discount!  Can you
      believe it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081297035264
    m_Localized: Porta Attendant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081401892864
    m_Localized: Oh, the smell?  It was like that when we bought the fleet of these.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081502556160
    m_Localized: Porta Attendant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081603219456
    m_Localized: ' I got this car freshener tree here to help freshen things up!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081703882752
    m_Localized: Monk Leader
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081804546048
    m_Localized: No no no, this isn't right.  You have far too much hair!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889081905209344
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082005872640
    m_Localized: Erk.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082106535936
    m_Localized: Monk Leader
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082207199232
    m_Localized: SO WHY ARE YOU HERE?!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082312056832
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082412720128
    m_Localized: Root Node to Skip
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082513383424
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082614046720
    m_Localized: '*Smooch* I''m so happy to see you.  You must have had a long day.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082714710016
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082819567616
    m_Localized: Why don't you have a bite to eat and head to bed?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889082920230912
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083020894208
    m_Localized: Good morning, sleepyhead!  Are you going to head into town today?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083121557504
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083222220800
    m_Localized: I'm thinking of getting one of those little robots to clean the
      house.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083327078400
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083427741696
    m_Localized: What are they called again?  Vwoomba?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083532599296
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083641651200
    m_Localized: I heard a cute new coffee shop opened up in town.  We should check
      it out sometime!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083746508800
    m_Localized: Lucy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083851366400
    m_Localized: Make sure you watch out for wild animals.  They've been straying
      closer to the paths lately.  Scary!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889083956224000
    m_Localized: Fashionable Girl
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084061081600
    m_Localized: Looks like I locked myself out again
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084170133504
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084274991104
    m_Localized: Mmmhmm?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084375654400
    m_Localized: Fashionable Girl
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084480512000
    m_Localized: Yeah, I mean, I swear this is my place
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084589563904
    m_Localized: Fashionable Girl
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084719587328
    m_Localized: What's it to ya anyway?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084837027840
    m_Localized: Counting Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889084967051264
    m_Localized: Root Node
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085084491776
    m_Localized: Counting Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085206126592
    m_Localized: One one thousand, two one thousand, three one thousand
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085323567104
    m_Localized: Counting Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085436813312
    m_Localized: . . . four one thousand, five one thousand, six one thousand
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085566836736
    m_Localized: Counting Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085684277248
    m_Localized: . . . seven one thousand, eight one thousand, nine one thousand
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085801717760
    m_Localized: Counting Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889085923352576
    m_Localized: . . . ten one thousand, eleven one thousand, twelve one thousand
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086040793088
    m_Localized: Counting Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086158233600
    m_Localized: . . . seventeen one thousand . . . wait, where was I?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086275674112
    m_Localized: Counting Guy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086393114624
    m_Localized: Shoot, you made me mess up, now I have to start all over again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086502166528
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086607024128
    m_Localized: Finally you've arrived.  My name is Phil, and I come bearing an
      urgent message.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086716076032
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086837710848
    m_Localized: Are you a talking cup of noodles?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889086959345664
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087080980480
    m_Localized: 'I may look like a delicious cup of noodles, but I''m actually a
      sophisticated artificial intelligence.  '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087198420992
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087315861504
    m_Localized: Wait . . . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087424913408
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087533965312
    m_Localized: What was that?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087643017216
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087760457728
    m_Localized: '. . . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087869509632
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889087974367232
    m_Localized: They must be moving faster than I thought.  We need to find some
      chopsticks immediately.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088087613440
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088196665344
    m_Localized: Once you find the chopsticks, you need to pour some hot water onto
      me and mush my noodles around.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088314105856
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088423157760
    m_Localized: '. . . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088528015360
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088632872960
    m_Localized: Errr?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088737730560
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088842588160
    m_Localized: Ok?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889088947445760
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089052303360
    m_Localized: I'm sorry, but now isn't the time to explain.  Quickly!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089152966656
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089257824256
    m_Localized: Default Text to Overwrite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089362681856
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089463345152
    m_Localized: There's one last step to the incantation.  You must find some extremely
      spicy hot sauce.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089568202752
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089668866048
    m_Localized: 'You have the hot sauce -- quick, squirt it into me.  '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089773723648
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089878581248
    m_Localized: Uhhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889089983438848
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090088296448
    m_Localized: Gross, no, not that way.  Just do it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090188959744
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090289623040
    m_Localized: I think they have some stocked in the convenience machines.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090398674944
    m_Localized: Sunbather
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090507726848
    m_Localized: Can you move?  You're blocking my sun
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090612584448
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090713247744
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090818105344
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889090922962944
    m_Localized: No
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091027820544
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091128483840
    m_Localized: Huh?  No, I don't need rescuing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091233341440
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091334004736
    m_Localized: I've just been trying to show these nerds how to do their job.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091438862336
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091543719936
    m_Localized: Anyway, let's get out of here Frankie, we have some work to do with
      Maya upstairs.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091644383232
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091749240832
    m_Localized: Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091849904128
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889091954761728
    m_Localized: Hey, uh, if you want down those stairs to the electrical room, you're
      gonna have to wrastle me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092059619328
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092164476928
    m_Localized: Do you want to wrastle me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092265140224
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092365803520
    m_Localized: Absolutely I do!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092470661120
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092575518720
    m_Localized: Thanks, um, I'll pass for now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092680376320
    m_Localized: Skilled Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092781039616
    m_Localized: Ah, my back!  You totally f***ed up my back!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092881702912
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889092986560512
    m_Localized: Default Text to Overwrite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093091418112
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093196275712
    m_Localized: '*squeak* I''m so stressed *squeak* these due dates are insane.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093301133312
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093405990912
    m_Localized: '*squeak* Oh, I''m so happy to see you.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093510848512
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093615706112
    m_Localized: 'It looks like everything is back to normal.  '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093716369408
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093821227008
    m_Localized: And my 401k is tanking . . . *sad squeak*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889093921890304
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094026747904
    m_Localized: How am I ever going to support my family like this? *desperate squeak*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094127411200
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094232268800
    m_Localized: Hmm
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094337126400
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094437789696
    m_Localized: Uhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094542647296
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094647504896
    m_Localized: '*squeak* I agree, Frankie.  We need to overthrow our capitalist
      overlords.  '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094748168192
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094848831488
    m_Localized: Erk
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889094953689088
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095058546688
    m_Localized: Uhhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095163404288
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095268261888
    m_Localized: Thanks for giving me this great advice.  *happy squeak* You're a
      real pal.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095373119488
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095473782784
    m_Localized: The power flickered, and then the interns went insane.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095578640384
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095683497984
    m_Localized: If anyone can sort this out, it's you.  Be careful! *inspiring squeak*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095788355584
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889095893213184
    m_Localized: It's like nobody even noticed the power went out.  Weird.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096006459392
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096115511296
    m_Localized: '*spooky squeak*'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096220368896
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096329420800
    m_Localized: Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096463638528
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096568496128
    m_Localized: Whoa whoa whoa, don't hurt me!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096673353728
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096774017024
    m_Localized: I may be bald, but I'm not one of these FREAKS.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096878874624
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889096983732224
    m_Localized: Hey, listen, if you need a way out of here, I can get you back to
      the PortaBank just outside the church.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097088589824
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097193447424
    m_Localized: Anyway, want to save your progress so far?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097298305024
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097403162624
    m_Localized: Yes, let's do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097508020224
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097617072128
    m_Localized: Nah, no thanks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097721929728
    m_Localized: Ron
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097826787328
    m_Localized: Want me to shuttle you back to the PortaBank?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889097927450624
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098036502528
    m_Localized: Nah, no thanks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098137165824
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098242023424
    m_Localized: Yes, get me out of here!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098346881024
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098455932928
    m_Localized: The comfy bed beckons . . . .
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098556596224
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098665648128
    m_Localized: Hello, comfy bed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098770505728
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098875363328
    m_Localized: Are you sure you want to go to sleep?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889098980220928
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099085078528
    m_Localized: Yeah
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099189936128
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099294793728
    m_Localized: No, I have work to do
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099399651328
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099504508928
    m_Localized: See you next time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099609366528
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099714224128
    m_Localized: Really?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099819081728
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889099923939328
    m_Localized: 'On second thought . . . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100028796928
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100137848832
    m_Localized: Yeah, I'm sure.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100246900736
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100351758336
    m_Localized: You can't take this back, you know?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100456615936
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100561473536
    m_Localized: I know.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100666331136
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100775383040
    m_Localized: Wait, I didn't mean it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100880240640
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889100985098240
    m_Localized: Ok.  See you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101089955840
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101199007744
    m_Localized: Frankie.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101303865344
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101412917248
    m_Localized: Can you help me out with this problem?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101517774848
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101622632448
    m_Localized: Okay
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101727490048
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101836541952
    m_Localized: No
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889101941399552
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102046257152
    m_Localized: You shouldn't spoil me too much, I'll never build up a real work
      ethic if you keep going on like this.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102151114752
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102255972352
    m_Localized: You're right.  I really need to take care of this myself.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102365024256
    m_Localized: Captivated Monk
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102469881856
    m_Localized: I've embraced my destiny.  Bald is power!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102578933760
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102683791360
    m_Localized: Hi there!  I'm not your enemy, merely a vole who wants to give you
      some advice!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102788648960
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102893506560
    m_Localized: In this demo you will face enemies of varying difficulty in order
      to gauge your combat prowess
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889102998364160
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103103221760
    m_Localized: Uh huh.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103208079360
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103312936960
    m_Localized: Yes, well, be warned!  Combat does not pause in Frankie!  Once an
      enemy can attack, they will!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103417794560
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103526846464
    m_Localized: To defeat your enemy, quickly select a skill using the directional
      UP-DOWN-LEFT-RIGHT or W-A-S-D keys, and lock it in using 'E'.  Then simply
      select your target and press 'E' again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103627509760
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103736561664
    m_Localized: As you gain new skills, you'll need to traverse deeper into your
      skill tree using the same directional keys.  Let's cross that bridge when we
      get there though!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103841419264
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889103946276864
    m_Localized: Mmmm.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104051134464
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104155992064
    m_Localized: OK!  That's it.  That's all, did you need me to repeat these instructions?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104265043968
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104365707264
    m_Localized: No
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104474759168
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104579616768
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104692862976
    m_Localized: Beautiful Tapestry
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104801914880
    m_Localized: Hello Francis
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889104915161088
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105061961728
    m_Localized: Are you speaking to me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105175207936
    m_Localized: Beautiful Tapestry
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105280065536
    m_Localized: Who else?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105389117440
    m_Localized: Beautiful Tapestry
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105498169344
    m_Localized: Do you want to join me, Francis??
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105615609856
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105728856064
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105837907968
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889105946959872
    m_Localized: Of course
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106056011776
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106165063680
    m_Localized: Uhhh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106274115584
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106383167488
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106496413696
    m_Localized: Beautiful Tapestry
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106605465600
    m_Localized: Bald is beautiful.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106714517504
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106823569408
    m_Localized: Bald
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889106932621312
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107041673216
    m_Localized: Bald is
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107150725120
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107259777024
    m_Localized: Bald is beautiful.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107368828928
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107477880832
    m_Localized: Wait!  I'm not gone yet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107586932736
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107695984640
    m_Localized: I have to know . . . are you team edward or team jacob?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107800842240
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889107909894144
    m_Localized: Oh.  Oh.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108018946048
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108127997952
    m_Localized: Nevermind, here it comes.  The great beyond.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108237049856
    m_Localized: Phil Ramen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108341907456
    m_Localized: Good luck, Frankie.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108450959360
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108560011264
    m_Localized: 'Hey, if you find yourself with a new piece for your outfit . .
      . '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108669063168
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108778115072
    m_Localized: Ya know, like a keyboard?  Or a vest?  Or a watch?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108887166976
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889108996218880
    m_Localized: Make sure you equip it in the Outfit menu!  It won't do any good
      just sitting in your knapsack unequipped!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109105270784
    m_Localized: Default
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109214322688
    m_Localized: Errr?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109323374592
    m_Localized: Estelle
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109432426496
    m_Localized: Oh, you're really fresh aren't you.  Access player menus by pressing
      the `TAB` key.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109537284096
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109646336000
    m_Localized: Hello again, Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109755387904
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109864439808
    m_Localized: Hello, comfy bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889109973491712
    m_Localized: Comfy Bed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110082543616
    m_Localized: Shall we?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110191595520
    m_Localized: Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110300647424
    m_Localized: Yes please
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110409699328
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110518751232
    m_Localized: Root node skipped
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110627803136
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110736855040
    m_Localized: Beat me and I'll tell you a secret.  *hue hue hue hue hue hue hue*
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110845906944
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889110954958848
    m_Localized: Hngh.  You really got me.  Alright, here's my secret.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111064010752
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111173062656
    m_Localized: After you've adventured a little, check your bank account.  You
      may be surprised to see your stocks have paid some dividends.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111277920256
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111391166464
    m_Localized: There's a PortaBank (TM) just outside this very office building.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111500218368
    m_Localized: Clever Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111609270272
    m_Localized: Question is, think you can take me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111718322176
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111827374080
    m_Localized: Nope.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889111936425984
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112045477888
    m_Localized: Yes?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112158724096
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112267776000
    m_Localized: Nah.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112376827904
    m_Localized: Tilly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112485879808
    m_Localized: Definitely not.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112590737408
    m_Localized: Maya
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112699789312
    m_Localized: GET.AWAY.FROM.MY.MICROWAVE.FRANKIE.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112808841216
    m_Localized: News Dude
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889112917893120
    m_Localized: Uh huh, uh huh, ok, uh huh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113026945024
    m_Localized: News Dude
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113135996928
    m_Localized: Yeah, uh huh, nuh uh, uh, huh, nuh uh
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113240854528
    m_Localized: News Dude
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113354100736
    m_Localized: Excuse me, could you hold on a minute?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113463152640
    m_Localized: News Dude
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113572204544
    m_Localized: Some brat is listening to my conversation
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113681256448
    m_Localized: News Dude
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113790308352
    m_Localized: Hey you - yeah, you - mind your own business!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889113903554560
    m_Localized: News Dude
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114012606464
    m_Localized: OK, where was I?  Uh huh, yeah, uhhh nuh uh, yeah huh.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114125852672
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114234904576
    m_Localized: It's me, your favourite friendly neighbourhood helpful vole!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114343956480
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114453008384
    m_Localized: Here's another tip!  You can change party order and add or remove
      party members by using the restroom in the office!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114562060288
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114671112192
    m_Localized: Of course, you need to have more than just YOU in the party, Frankie!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114780164096
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889114893410304
    m_Localized: That's all for now!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115002462208
    m_Localized: Helpful Vole
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115111514112
    m_Localized: Squeak!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115224760320
    m_Localized: Default
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115338006528
    m_Localized: Default Text to Overwrite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115451252736
    m_Localized: Horse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115560304640
    m_Localized: We're so proud of what you've accomplished here.  You're really
      an A++ Worker.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115673550848
    m_Localized: Horse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115782602752
    m_Localized: We can't wait to see what you'll do next.  Keep on truckin'!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889115891654656
    m_Localized: Horse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116000706560
    m_Localized: Now that I've sufficiently complimented you, I need you to do me
      a favor.  Maya has some *VERY IMPORTANT DOCUMENTS*.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116109758464
    m_Localized: Horse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116218810368
    m_Localized: Thanks for deliverying these *VERY IMPORTANT DOCUMENTS*.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116327862272
    m_Localized: Horse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116436914176
    m_Localized: I must now further examine these *VERY IMPORTANT DOCUMENTS*.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116545966080
    m_Localized: Horse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116659212288
    m_Localized: You may take your 15 minute break -- I've enabled elevator access
      to the kitchen.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116768264192
    m_Localized: Horse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116877316096
    m_Localized: Please hop down that firepole -- yes, the one that says DANGER on
      it -- and find the documents.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889116990562304
    m_Localized: Horse
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117099614208
    m_Localized: Any luck?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117208666112
    m_Localized: Generic Office Worker Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117321912320
    m_Localized: Frankie Frankie Frankie Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117430964224
    m_Localized: Generic Office Worker Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117540016128
    m_Localized: My name is Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117649068032
    m_Localized: Generic Office Worker Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117758119936
    m_Localized: That's kind of like Frankie
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117871366144
    m_Localized: Generic Office Worker Fran
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889117980418048
    m_Localized: Am I you?  Are you me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118089469952
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118198521856
    m_Localized: Skip Root
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118307573760
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118416625664
    m_Localized: Oh no oh no oh no oh no.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118525677568
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118634729472
    m_Localized: Frankie!  I need your help, I really messed up this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118743781376
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118852833280
    m_Localized: I dared Tilly to hop down the fireman's pole in the ballpit room
      and SHE DID.  Now she's trapped with the interns.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889118961885184
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119075131392
    m_Localized: Look, Horse locked the door to the ballpit room, but you can make
      your way down to Tilly in the basement with the elevator.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119184183296
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119293235200
    m_Localized: Come on Frankie, please go find Tilly.  She'll kill me if we just
      leave her down there.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119406481408
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119515533312
    m_Localized: Oh, uh, hi Tilly.  Good to uh . . . see you again . . . in good
      spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119624585216
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119737831424
    m_Localized: Thanks Frankie, I really owe ya one.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119846883328
    m_Localized: Bro Office Worker
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2889119955935232
    m_Localized: Watch out for the interns, they're really riled up about something.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
